    <item>
      <title>英国亨特表示，高通胀时期已经过去</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/period-of-high-inflation-is-behind-us-says-uk-s-hunt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特表示，经济增长前景非常强劲，高通胀时期“确实已经过去”。他在纽约接受了彭博社的 Kailey Leinz 的采访。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/period-of-high-inflation-is-behind-us-says-uk-s-hunt</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 18:44:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德克萨斯州市政借款人哀叹限制银行的反 ESG 法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/texas-muni-borrowers-bemoan-anti-esg-laws-restricting-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州的借款人聚集在一次行业会议上，对该州的两项共和党支持的法律表示遗憾，发行人称这些法律限制了他们可以与哪些华尔街银行开展业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/texas-muni-borrowers-bemoan-anti-esg-laws-restricting-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 18:26:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯·格里芬 (Ken Griffin) 押注纽约 62 层曼哈顿大厦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/ken-griffin-bets-on-nyc-with-62-story-manhattan-tower-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社的 Natalie Wong 报道，肯·格里芬正在推进公园大道 62 层摩天大楼的计划，加深他对纽约市的承诺。这座塔楼的 Griffin&#39;s Citadel 和 Citadel 证券的空间至少是这两家公司目前在附近建筑中占用的空间的两倍。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/ken-griffin-bets-on-nyc-with-62-story-manhattan-tower-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 18:14:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织改变贷款规则以加速债务重组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/imf-board-changes-lending-rules-to-speed-up-debt-restructuring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织执行董事会投票决定改革其支持债务重组的程序，允许债务重组计划在债权人抵制的情况下继续推进。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/imf-board-changes-lending-rules-to-speed-up-debt-restructuring</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 18:07:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔表示通胀意外后将推迟降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/powell-signals-high-rates-for-longer-due-to-persistent-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，在一系列令人惊讶的高通胀数据之后，政策制定者降息的时间将比之前预期的要长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/powell-signals-high-rates-for-longer-due-to-persistent-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 17:38:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉股价跌破 5000 亿美元，对股市多头造成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/tesla-s-value-declines-below-500-billion-as-risks-pile-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉股价在 2024 年延续跌势，导致这家电动汽车制造商的市值跌破 5000 亿美元，本周的一轮裁员凸显了该公司增长放缓的程度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/tesla-s-value-declines-below-500-billion-as-risks-pile-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 13:41:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水务将于本周发布更新的业务计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/thames-water-to-release-updated-business-plan-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务公用事业有限公司的董事会成员将于本周进行最后一次谈判，以更新其业务计划，此前股东称前一项计划“不可投资”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/thames-water-to-release-updated-business-plan-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:02:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储推迟降息，美元有望创年内最佳表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/usd-dollar-heads-for-best-run-in-year-in-bet-on-fed-delaying-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预期美国利率将在更长时间内保持在高位，并且随着中东紧张局势不断升级，投资者纷纷涌入避险货币，美元将迎来一年多以来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/usd-dollar-heads-for-best-run-in-year-in-bet-on-fed-delaying-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 09:31:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鹰派鲍威尔加息 5%，美国收益率飙升：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的债券市场再次遭受重创，由于杰罗姆·鲍威尔暗示政策制定者不急于降息，两年期国债收益率一度触及5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 22:18:48 GMT</pubDate>
